{
  "stem": "1684.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 425.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because they knew Tisch's word was very, very important.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we were on the list to go to Brunnlitz.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, Plaszow was terrible.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I can tell you about Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In Plaszow, first of all, I got once very sick.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I had a very high fever, and I went into the krankenstube.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now, as sick as I was, I didn't want to stay there, because they-- they knew that, God forbid, if you stayed there a little longer, you might get to Auschwitz, they would take you out anyhow.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "One day, it was a very, very, a cold day.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was in May.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And Mengele-- Dr.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Mengele from-- from Auschwitz came, with some other guys, and they had tables set up.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we had stand there naked.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "All-- everybody was naked.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they had like files with paper.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And everybody had to march down the aisles.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And Mengele was looking you over.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I was lucky, I wasn't on the-- I mean, they did not take my name.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But if he saw somebody who was a little fragile looking, or so, they just put the number on it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We had numbers.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And the next day they came and they took them to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "That was in Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Another thing was in Plaszow, one day they all called us down.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And there were big loudspeakers in Plaszow, on-- on the appellplatz.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And they were-- the children who were saved by Schindler-- because he had a factory outside from Plaszow for a while in Krakow-- and these kids were saved.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "There were maybe by 300 children or so.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "There was a big truck.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And the truck came and took all the children away.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And they were singing a lullaby on the loudspeaker-- good evening, goodnight.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "In German, of course.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
